CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779891067
OL,3,CDozens killed as Israel ramps up
OL,4,Cstrikes on Lebanon despite ceasefire
OL,6,FDozens of people have been killed in a
OL,7,Fwave of Israeli airstrikes on Lebanon
OL,8,Fovernight, after Benjamin Netanyahu
OL,9,Fsaid the military was "deepening its
OL,10,Foperation" against Hezbollah.
OL,12,FThe Lebanese Ministry of Public Health
OL,13,Fsaid 31 people were killed in the
OL,14,Flatest attacks, including four
OL,15,Fchildren and three women.
OL,17,FThe Israel Defence Forces (IDF) said
OL,18,Fit struck more than 100 Hezbollah
OL,19,Fsites across southern Lebanon and the
OL,20,Feastern Bekaa Valley area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779891067
OL,3,CDozens killed as Israel ramps up
OL,4,Cstrikes on Lebanon despite ceasefire
OL,6,FIt added that it targeted storage
OL,7,Ffacilities, command centres and
OL,8,Fobservation points, which it says were
OL,9,Fused to attack Israeli troops and
OL,10,Fresidents in northern Israel.
OL,12,FOne Israeli strike killed a family of
OL,13,F12 in the eastern village of
OL,14,FMashghara, Lebanon's state-run
OL,15,FNational News Agency said.
OL,17,FThe latest wave of strikes on Lebanon
OL,18,Fcomes despite a ceasefire, brokered by
OL,19,Fthe US and agreed upon by Israel and
OL,20,FLebanon in mid-April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779891067
OL,3,CDozens killed as Israel ramps up
OL,4,Cstrikes on Lebanon despite ceasefire
OL,6,FDespite being one of the main fighting
OL,7,Fforces involved in this strand of the
OL,8,FMiddle East conflict, Hezbollah, which
OL,9,Fis backed by Iran and is one of the
OL,10,Fworld's most powerful non-state
OL,11,Factors, was not a signatory to the
OL,12,Fagreement.
OL,14,FThe Shia militant group does not
OL,15,Frecognise the ceasefire and has
OL,16,Fdismissed it as "meaningless" in light
OL,17,Fof continued Israeli attacks and
OL,18,Fdemolition of communities in the south.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779891067
OL,3,CDozens killed as Israel ramps up
OL,4,Cstrikes on Lebanon despite ceasefire
OL,6,FIsraeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,7,FNetanyahu warned on Monday that the
OL,8,Fmilitary would "intensify the blows"
OL,9,Fand "increase the force" of their
OL,10,Fcampaign in Lebanon.
OL,12,FDonald Trump is due to meet his
OL,13,FCabinet later on Wednesday, just days
OL,14,Fafter the US' latest attacks on Tehran.
OL,16,FOver the weekend, Trump said his
OL,17,Fadministration and Iran had "largely
OL,18,Fnegotiated" a settlement.
OL,26,@pD@POUpD@dO]qD@EOUqD@XO]yD@]OUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779891067
OL,3,CDozens killed as Israel ramps up
OL,4,Cstrikes on Lebanon despite ceasefire
OL,6,FElsewhere in eastern Lebanon, Israel
OL,7,Fstruck an area near the Qaraoun Dam,
OL,8,Fthe country's largest along the Litani
OL,9,FRiver. The Litani River Authority said
OL,10,Fthere was no direct damage to the dam.
OL,12,FClashes between the IDF and Iran-
OL,13,Fbacked Hezbollah militants along the
OL,14,Fstrategic Litani River in southern
OL,15,FLebanon come just days before Lebanese
OL,16,Fand Israeli delegates are due to meet
OL,17,Ffor talks in Washington.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779891067
OL,3,CDozens killed as Israel ramps up
OL,4,Cstrikes on Lebanon despite ceasefire
OL,6,FTehran has insisted it wants any peace
OL,7,Fdeal agreed upon for the wider Middle
OL,8,FEast conflict between the US and Iran
OL,9,Fto include an end to fighting in
OL,10,FLebanon.
OL,12,FThis does not appear to be on Israel's
OL,13,Fagenda, however, with Netanyahu
OL,14,Fdeclaring after a meeting with his
OL,15,Fdefence minister and senior military
OL,16,Fofficials that Israel will expand its
OL,17,Foperations in Lebanon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779891067
OL,3,CDozens killed as Israel ramps up
OL,4,Cstrikes on Lebanon despite ceasefire
OL,6,FThe Litani River has been a de facto
OL,7,Fboundary in Lebanon, with large areas
OL,8,Fto the south under Israeli military
OL,9,Fcontrol despite the ceasefire that's
OL,10,Fbeen in place for over a month.
OL,12,FIsrael, in recent days, has
OL,13,Fintensified strikes in the city and
OL,14,Fprovince of Nabatiyeh, just north of
OL,15,Fthe river and warned city residents to
OL,16,Fleave on Tuesday.
OL,18,F"The IDF is operating with large
OL,19,Fforces on the ground and seizing
OL,20,Fstrategic areas," Netanyahu said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779891067
OL,3,CDozens killed as Israel ramps up
OL,4,Cstrikes on Lebanon despite ceasefire
OL,6,FHe added that Israel is trying to
OL,7,Ffortify an area of southern Lebanon
OL,8,Funder its control, which it says is
OL,9,Fnecessary to protect residents in its
OL,10,Fnorthern border towns from Hezbollah
OL,11,Fattacks.
OL,13,FBeirut, the Lebanese capital, has been
OL,14,Fspared from strikes since the start of
OL,15,Fthe ceasefire, but Israel's latest
OL,16,Fmoves have caused fear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779891067
OL,3,CDozens killed as Israel ramps up
OL,4,Cstrikes on Lebanon despite ceasefire
OL,6,F"By just saying a few words on TV,
OL,7,F(Netanyahu) causes everyone to panic
OL,8,Fand flee their homes," said Tony Aboud
OL,9,Fin Beirut's bustling Hamra district.
OL,10,F"I don't know what's going to happen
OL,11,Fand how long we can live like this."
OL,13,FHezbollah, meanwhile, said it launched
OL,14,Fseveral rockets, artillery and
OL,15,Fexploding drone attacks on Israeli
OL,16,Ftroops and vehicles mobilising along
OL,17,Fthe river toward the Nabatiyeh
OL,18,Fvillages of Yohmor al-Shaqif and
OL,19,FZawtar al-Sharqieh.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@VO]rD@AOUsD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779891067
OL,3,CDozens killed as Israel ramps up
OL,4,Cstrikes on Lebanon despite ceasefire
OL,6,FHezbollah's Al-Manar TV said the
OL,7,Fmilitant group repelled attacks along
OL,8,Fthe river banks.
OL,10,FOn the question of whether or not to
OL,11,Finclude Lebanon in any ceasefire
OL,12,Fagreement negotiated with the United
OL,13,FStates, Donald Trump's administration
OL,14,Fappears to have left some wiggle room.
OL,16,FThe draft agreement proposes a
OL,17,Fceasefire between the US and its
OL,18,Fallies and Iran and its proxies, such
OL,19,Fas Hezbollah. It also makes clear that
OL,20,FIsrael can act to stop immediate
OL,21,Fthreats and defend itself.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779891067
OL,3,CDozens killed as Israel ramps up
OL,4,Cstrikes on Lebanon despite ceasefire
OL,6,FJonathan Conricus, a former IDF
OL,7,Fspokesperson, said Israel expects that
OL,8,FIran would quickly move to direct any
OL,9,Fsanctions relief to restore its
OL,10,Fmilitary capability and boost proxy
OL,11,Fgroups, including Hezbollah and Hamas
OL,12,Fin Gaza.
OL,14,F"We're not done fighting, because the
OL,15,FIranian regime isn't done," said
OL,16,FConricus, who is a senior fellow with
OL,17,Fthe Foundation for Defense of
OL,18,FDemocracies, a hawkish Washington
OL,19,Fthink tank.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
