OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779891067
OL,3,CDozens killed as Israel ramps up
OL,4,Cstrikes on Lebanon despite ceasefire
OL,6,FTrump recently told Netanyahu he
OL,7,Fsupports the country's wish to
OL,8,F"maintain freedom of action against
OL,9,Fthreats on all fronts, including
OL,10,FLebanon," an Israeli official told ITV
OL,11,FNews' North American partner CNN.
OL,13,FIn a call with Netanyahu on Saturday
OL,14,Fevening, Trump "reiterated his support
OL,15,Ffor this principle", the official said.
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@IO]vD@POUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
