CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779891067
OL,3,CDozens killed as Israel ramps up
OL,4,Cstrikes on Lebanon despite ceasefire
OL,6,FUltimately, Iran insists it is ready
OL,7,Ffor a "fair and balanced deal," the
OL,8,FIranian source told CNN Sunday. "The
OL,9,Fmost important thing for us is that
OL,10,Fthe war must end for good in the whole
OL,11,FMiddle East."
